2
00:00:09.119 --> 00:00:10.179
to proper swallowing.

3
00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:12.659
Why is this important?

4
00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:15.548
Because if a child
swallows incorrectly,

5
00:00:15.559 --> 00:00:16.359
they will tense up.

6
00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:18.239
The tongue will
begin to tense up.

7
00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.928
The lips will also tense,
and the neck will become

8
00:00:20.939 --> 00:00:21.939
quite tense as well.

9
00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:25.619
And as a result of this, an
incorrect bite will form.

10
00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:31.627
Your speech will become
strained, and the skull bones

11
00:00:31.639 --> 00:00:35.099
will shift, which will lead
to an unattractive face.

12
00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:38.468
Naturally, we all want our
children to grow up to be

13
00:00:38.479 --> 00:00:39.859
both beautiful and healthy.

14
00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:44.009
That is exactly why, in this
lesson, we will dive much

15
00:00:44.020 --> 00:00:45.179
deeper into this topic.

